    "text": [
        "Dear Sir/ Madam,",
        "I am writing this letter referring to the advertisement I saw in a weekend magazine which was regarding a child caretaker.",
        "This opportunity will be ideal for me due to various reasons. The first reason is that I love to spend my time with kids since it provides me pleasure. In addition to that, currently I am studying in my final semester of the degree and I wanted to do a job which does not affect for my studies as well as to have a considerable financial benefit.",
        "I  will be a good match to your requirement because I am following a child care degree program which provided me practical exposure in handling a three year old child 6 months ago. Moreover, I will be able to help your kid with school work since I am also learning these days.",
        "I prefer to spend my free time by exploring the city. However, in coming six months, most probably I will stay at home because I have my final semester exams.",
        "I am expecting for a favourable reply from you.",
        "Yours Faithfully,",
        "Thuya Perera"
